description: This file defines an enum class `MacroType` representing different macro types used in macro substitution, including methods to get the macro type from command strings.

classes.name: MacroType
classes.description: An enumeration of macro types (IF, ELSE, ELSE_IF, END) used in macro substitution and a static method to get the macro type from a command string.

methods.name: getForCommand
methods.description: Returns the corresponding MacroType for a given command string, case-insensitive, or null if no match.
